        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Memorandum of duties.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>I wish <persName>Mr Williams </persName>to sleep in my <placeName>house </placeName>while I am gone and
take special care of everything particularly the corn and meat and
the two motherless pigs&#8212;also to set <persName>Dolly</persName>, <persName>Patsy</persName>, and <persName>Henry </persName>to
piling the pumpkins and covering them with corn stacks&#8212;keep the
crib and <placeName>smoke House</placeName> locked&#8212;make out a number of blank deeds
for individual transfers&#8212;and take care <hi rend="italic">office</hi></p>

<p><date when="1824-11-18">Novr. 18. 1824</date></p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName></p>

        </div1>
